{"id":189322,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/维权网-广西律师案：裴日红案10月14日开庭/","date":"2011-10-17T05:31:02Z","modified":"2013-02-06T10:25:53Z","title":"维权网 | 广西律师案：“裴日红案”10月14日开庭","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><b><span>      </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></span><b><span>（维权网信息员金正方报道）</span></b><span>明天（<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>日）上午<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>时，北海市中级人民法院将开庭审理“裴日红等<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>人故意伤害案”，庭审时间为七天，至<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>日结束。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日，北海律师团成员陆续抵达广西北海。至<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>日上午，</span><span>杨金柱、覃永沛、王</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>兴、周</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>泽、徐天明等律师已经会见了各自的当事人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>几名当事人在会见时，对律师讲述了被刑讯逼供的经历。其中，黄子富说被海城区公安分局刑侦大队警察电击，而杨炳棋被捆绑后挂在窗户上。杨炳棋对律师说，“如果我死在看守所，一定是他们逼死的”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“裴日红等<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>人故意伤害案”直接导致“广西四律师伪证案”的发生，因此备受各界关注。今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月中旬，</span><span>北京、山东、云南、陕西、广东、湖南等地的二十余名律师自发组成律师团，前往北海市为当事人提供法律援助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>律师团从“裴日红等故意伤害案”入手，全面介入北海系列案件。今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月以来，北海中级法院先后四次确定开庭时间（<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>日），前三次均延期，而第四次仅开庭一天即宣布休庭。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>该案的被告分别是裴日红、裴金德、裴贵、杨炳棋、黄子富等五人。他们被指控将黄焕海殴打致死，并抛尸大海。案件疑点重重，刑讯逼供的印迹随处可见。不管是之前被以“伪证罪”抓捕的杨在新律师，还是之后律师团的十名律师均为五名被告人作无罪辩护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网将持续关注该案的庭审情况。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨金柱律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13908460728</span></span></div>\n<div><span>王<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span></span>兴律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13691192655</span></span></div>\n<div><span>覃永沛律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13036818838</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5888009211059973928?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[22167,9377,8906]}